A
\int_A f(x) d \mu \ge 0
f
\int_A f(x) d\mu = \lim\limits_{n \rightarrow \infty} \int_{A} f_n(x) d\mu
f_n
f
f_n = -1/n
f = 0
f_n \ge 0
f_n \nearrow f
\int_A f d\mu = \lim_{n\to\infty} \underbrace{\int_A f_n d\mu}_{\ge 0} \ge 0
f\ge g\Rightarrow \int f\ge \int g 
\int f = \sup\{\int s|s, simple\}=\sup\{\int s|s, simple,positive\}
